Didn't I say I'd draw late into the night so wake me up?

39
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:38,000
<i>[Wake up, Nuan Nuan! From loving Sister Xin Ran and hateful Zhao Ming Yang]</i>

40
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:41,400
